    "headline": "2026年国际邀请赛直邀和预选赛",
    "posttime": 1779766203,
    "updatetime": 1779766203,
    "body": [
      "[img]{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/3703047/1477d1a3748ef268c4b431dd4af64cf4ad8ffdd7.png[/img]",
      "[p]这一年下来，全世界的Dota战队都在努力征战，只为证明自己有资格受邀参加国际邀请赛——在全球最大的舞台上争夺冠军之神盾。 获得邀请的队伍可以开始专注于最后的准备，而剩下的挑战者还有最后一个拼搏的机会。[/p]",
      "[h3]直接邀请[/h3]",
      "[p]距离大赛开幕还有不到三个月，我们很高兴邀请以下七支队伍，前往中国上海参加2026年国际邀请赛：[/p]",
      "[list]",
      "[*]Aurora Gaming",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "Egor \"Nightfall\" Grigorenko",
      "Rafli \"Mikoto\" Fathur Rahman",
      "Wei Shen \"Ws`\" Chung",
      "Myroslav \"Mira\" Kolpakov",
      "Oleh \"kaori\" Medvedok",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*]BoomBoys",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "Ilia \"Kiritych~\" Ulianov",
      "Danil \"gpk~\" Skutin",
      "Matvei \"MieRo`\" Vasiunin",
      "Vitalie \"Save-\" Melnic",
      "Vladislav \"Kataomi`\" Semenov",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*]Team Falcons",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "Oliver \"Skiter\" Lepko",
      "Stanislav \"Malr1ne\" Potorak",
      "Ammar \"ATF\" Alassaf",
      "Andreas \"Cr1t-\" Nielsen",
      "Jingjun \"Sneyking\" Wu",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*]Team Liquid",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "Michael \"m1CKe\" Vu",
      "Michał \"Nisha\" Jankowski",
      "Marcus \"Ace\" Christensen",
      "Samuel \"Boxi\" Svahn",
      "Erik \"tOfu\" Engel",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*]Tundra Esports",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "Ivan \"Pure\" Moskalenko",
      "Bozhidar \"bzm\" Bogdanov",
      "Neta \"33\" Shapira",
      "Matthew \"Ari\" Walker",
      "Matthew \"Whitemon\" Filemon",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*]Xtreme Gaming",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "Chunyu \"Ame\" Wang",
      "Jin Xiang \"NothingToSay\" Cheng",
      "Jing \"Xxs\" Lin",
      "Linsen \"fy\" Xu",
      "Jian Wei \"xNova\" Yap",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*]Team Yandex",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "Alimzhan \"医者watson\" Islambekov",
      "Ilya \"CHIRA_JUNIOR\" Chirtsov",
      "Dmitrii \"DM\" Dorokhin",
      "Martin \"Saksa\" Sazdov",
      "Arman \"Malady\" Orazbayev",
      "[/expand]",
      "[/list]",
      "[h3]地区预选赛[/h3][p]",
      "以上的七支队伍均获得了直接邀请的参赛名额，这意味着TI还剩下九个名额，只有经受住地区预选赛的严酷考验，才能收入囊中。 今年东欧和西欧预选赛合并为欧洲预选赛，四个参赛名额。 请查看下方完整的赛程安排。[/p]",
      "[list][*][b]中国[/b]，6月15日至18日（2个名额）",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "Vici Gaming",
      "Roar Gaming",
      "Yakutou Brothers",
      "Team Resilience",
      "[i] （+4支公开预选赛队伍）[/i]",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*][b]南美[/b]，6月15-19日 （1个名额）",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "LGD Gaming",
      "PlayTime",
      "Estar Backs",
      "Red Hot Chili Pibble",
      "Amaru Gaming",
      "Hokori",
      "[i] （+4支公开预选赛队伍）[/i]",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*][b]东南亚[/b]，6月19-23日 （1个名额）",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "REKONIX",
      "OG",
      "Execration",
      "Team Nemesis",
      "GLYPH",
      "[i] （+5支公开预选赛队伍）[/i]",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*][b]欧洲[/b]，6月21-28日（4个名额）",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "TEAM VISION",
      "Team Spirit",
      "MOUZ",
      "Natus Vincere",
      "Nigma Galaxy",
      "Virtus.Pro",
      "enjoy",
      "Power Rangers",
      "[i] （+8支公开预选赛队伍）[/i]",
      "[/expand]",
      "[*][b]北美[/b]，6月24-26日 （1个名额）",
      "[expand type=details]",
      "GamerLegion",
      "[i] （+3支公开预选赛队伍）[/i]",
      "[/expand]",
      "[/list]",
      "[p]6月28日预选赛全部结束后，所有参赛队伍都将尘埃落定。下一站，上海。 小组赛将于8月13日至16日拉开帷幕，前三天是五轮瑞士轮的比赛，接着在周日会有五场淘汰赛。 晋级的八支队伍会在8月20-23日进入场馆，角逐冠军之神盾。[/p]"
